name: @ionic-native/touch-id
readme: Improve this doc # Touch ID ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-touch-id $ npm install --save @ionic-native/touch-id ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/touch-id/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/EddyVerbruggen/cordova-plugin-touch-id](https://github.com/EddyVerbruggen/cordova-plugin-touch-id) Scan the fingerprint of a user with the TouchID sensor. Requires Cordova plugin: `cordova-plugin-touch-id`. For more info, please see the [TouchID plugin docs](https://github.com/EddyVerbruggen/cordova-plugin-touch-id). ## Supported platforms - iOS
